<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (zy bḥr bdwn myạh .. zy qlb bdwn ḥyạẗ
 ḥyạty mn gẖyr yswʿ
 zy sẖms bdwn ḍyạʾ .. zy ḥb bdwn ʿṭạʾ
 ḥyạty mn gẖyr yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ḥbk lyã yạ rby .. zy ạlbḥr gẖạmrny
 gẖṭạny lḥd rạsy .. wmạfysẖ klạm ywfyh)2
 2- (lw mạfysẖ klmẗ bmʿạny .. lw mạfysẖ lḥn ạlạ̉gẖạny
 msẖ hạyskt qlby lyk
 lw sẖʿwb ạldnyạ wqft .. ʿlsẖạn tsbyḥy yskt
 brḍh hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny lyk)2</lyrics>
<title>zy bḥr bdwn myạh</title>
</song>